name: Moon Raider: First Landing
description:
An arcade game you can play in your web browser. Compete to achieve the highest score #moonraider

You make it to the moon only to run into a species of deadly space rats.

Controls: Keyboard Only (Use Whichever layout works best for you)
Jump: Up, W, Z
Hover (hold): Up, Left, Down, W, A, S, Shift
Shoot: Right, D, X
